Name: OutputDatasetName
Description: The name of a new, aggregated dataset to be created.

Name: GroupByVariables
Description: Variables used as keys to identify groups.

Name: AggregateVariables
Description: The expressions that compute the aggregations. An aggregation function should be used.

Name: Weighting
Description: Description of the weights to be used

Name: CaseWise
Description: Observations are not included if any variable  is missing

Name: ColumnWise
Description: Variables are not included if any value in a column is missing
